Subject: Received error message upgrading to 5.9.4.1
Description:
Received the following error after update failure:

"Some problems occurred during installation. Please Contact Support. (ERROR: 2 - Number of maximum retries for this update reached, skipping this update...)"
What_We_Know__c:
- Client experienced error message upgrading to 5.9.4.1

Please Contact Support. (ERROR: 2 - Number of maximum retries for this update reached, skipping this update...)

- Sent out email to client to reattempt the upgrade to 5.9.4.1

- 1/10/2025 Client responded back with scheduled a patch window for today afternoon
Solution_Comment__c: Customer has applied EPP update to 5.9.4.1 and has agreed to close the ticket.
